node.text: @artisansdegeneve introducing the new series “Meet the Passion” and today met and interviewed John Demsey, Executive Group President of Estee Lauder,  he opens up about his  passion for fine art, customization and watchmaking

In the making with the magical @jacobandco Opera Godfather in the all new suit 🌐
The Opera Godfather now comes in a new 49mm rose gold or black ceramic and domed sapphire crystal case, the large size allowing for the placement of two barrels hand-set with 666 brilliant white diamonds (approx. 1.85 cts) specially crafted to reproduce the music. Here a brief passage of the supreme gem setting art of Jacob's artisans.
The triple axis tourbillon dances it’s round-the-clock mechanical ballet.
Limited edition of 88 pieces worldwide

node.text:
Cristiano Ronaldo, officially a Man United player for a few days already, made his first appearance in the city wearing a custom Rolex Cosmograph Daytona 116508 in 18k yellow gold with aftermarket rainbow sapphires bezel. The mother of pearl dial features brilliant-cut diamonds as hour markers and champagne chronograph sub-dials. The Portuguese used this same watch during euro 2020
•
📸 edit @vertigo1983

Ice blue hat trick 🤟🏻
Spot a favorite?👀
•
📸 @gwatchg

node.text:
The Danish personal trainer, fitness model and social media celebrity Mia Sand @missmiafit is wearing a platinum 40mm Rolex Cosmograph Daytona with brown cerachrome bezel and ice blue dial. Released at Baselworld 2013 for the 50th anniversary of this legendary chronograph, it was the first time that this model was entirely made in platinum.
⌚️tag price: $74,800.00
